Usage

1. Download and install jME SDK 3 : http://hub.jmonkeyengine.org/downloads/
2. Open the project contained in this repository
3. To indicate where your android SDK is, right click on the project, go to Properties, under Application/Android click "Run Android Target Configuration Utility"
4. Build (android and native) using the hammer icon
5. Run the desktop application with "<default confid>", the android one with "Android Device"
6. You need tag #1023 and another to see something happen: 1023 is the reference, any other tag moves the object.
